reviews.text: Good 肉骨茶🍵 (pork ribs in medicinal soup) for cold winter afternoon. The pork ribs taste fresh and might be from local market (?). Could do better with having fresh barley water as there was not much pandan taste and make it available fresh and hot in a cup for cold days. Dishes should also come with more veggies but you can order veggies on the side (a bit on the pricey side for the boiled veggies).
Very nice Hainan Chicken Rice and Marinated Pig Trotter. Not much comfort but i went there for the food. Very convenient if you are driving as there are plenty of space around the shop.
Food quality is fantastic. However, there is not table and you might hope to go there earlier before the peak hour for queuing for seats.
only if i am in a hurry. not quite wgat i expected though. friendly people.
okay at reasonable price

result.name: 肥仔海南雞

reviews.text: 錯的選擇

肥仔海南雞飯，$32來講份量已算多，連埋個冬瓜湯，用來做下午茶晚餐其實都好夠。尤其是係女仔添！其實我覺得佢嘅組合好彈性，可以加錢加雞肉， 加雞腎，或者加雞翼。收費唔算貴平民消費。味道都唔錯，最值得一讚嘅係佢嘅水準每日都keep到。平時食開都唔覺得佢嘅質素唔會有太大改變。

之前我都試過佢娘惹咖喱牛筋腩飯，其實都唔錯幾好食，咖喱係有少少辣有啲牛腩同牛筋味道都真係唔錯，有咬口但係唔係咬唔開嗰種。

元朗嘅小舖真係好多，但係做得長做得久真係好少。這一間小舖基本上我每星期都會幫襯兩至三次，睇得出依間野嘅食品係有心做，雖然選擇少，好食保持到水準其實係最緊要！
只有三樣食物 海南雞  豬手飯和牛南飯
舊了些，食物不錯
海南雞飯非常美味，而且價格相宜。
